data.description: Stunning 4BR, 3FB, 3LVL SFH Located in Newington Woods Close to Springfield Metro! Lots of Updates to This Home ~ HVAC '15, Recessed Lighting In Living & Dining Rooms '18 & Master Bedroom, Lower Level 3rd FB '14, New Massive Back Porch ‘20, New Roof & Gutters '22, New HWH '22, & so Much More! Gourmet Kitchen w/Granite Counters & Updated Appliances. Beautiful Hardwoods on Main Level & in all bedrooms to include MBR! Perfect Backyard for Entertaining w/Decking & Flagstone Patio! New expanded driveway increases available parking from two cars to four!
data.whatILove: Quiet, family friendly community with awesome, welcoming and helpful neighbors. Extremely easy commuting options to Pentagon--easy access for "slug" lines, 3/4 mile to commuter lot and rush hour bus service.  Very close access to metro options.  Located 7 miles from Fort Belvoir. Easy lawn maintenance--perennials galore..You can mow the lawn in under 20 minutes.  Custom Fence with copper toppings in back patio for complete privacy.  Custom designed back porch reflects easy entertaining style with extra wide top railing.  Backyard patio reduces lawn maintenance.
